name: [Guest user][.com]Place order using shipping methods - BOPIS, STM

steps.name: Given Guest User should be on michaels home page
When user adds products with "Store Pickup ,Ship to Me" shipping method to the cart
And User should click on checkout button
And User will get model popup to click on continue as guest user
When User should provides shipping information like Valid First Name, Last Name,Addressline1 Addressline2,city,state,zipcode,email and Phone number
And validate product details on checkout page
When the user selects the PayPal payment method in the payment review page
Then the user should be logged in successfully to the PayPal account
And the user should land on the order confirmation page post PayPal payment
